snippet.title: Help Me Now ( Announcement trailer #3)
snippet.description:
This game is based on horror and suspense, where an investigative detective is assigned a mission to explore an isolated house in southern Arizona. This game has several mechanics!
They are: batteries present in your flashlight, you will need to take care of your hunger, thirst, stamina and health to survive the non-terrifying house where the game is located! In addition, this game features multi-end mechanics and jumpscars.
